86, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"a last dance\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after 15 years and an Olympic medal, next week's world figure skating championships look a lot like a victory lap.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"15 years\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"next week's world figure skating championships\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory lap\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian ice dancers will arrive in Prague after winning bronze with a euphoric free skate at last month's Milan Cortina Winter Games, the culmination of a career built slowly - and on their own terms.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999607081538328, \"rank\": 3.9292404536950836e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 442, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"score\": 0.9981415865995672, \"rank\": 0.001861847371944663, \"text\": \"Prague\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"score\": 0.8153954872814404, \"rank\": 0.2263987421954181, \"text\": \"Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4770570429352806e-15, \"text\": \"Cortina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\"