"to\": 1666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think we intended to be that content after a program,\\\" Gilles said during a conference call Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that content\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"a program\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"Gilles\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"a conference call\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have always been like, 'OK, we won this event, or we have medalled at this event, now we have something else to look forward to.'\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think, we just allowed ourselves to be so present in that moment.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were not ready to leave that moment ... even when we got to the podium, we were like, 'We could stay on this podium forever.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"this podium\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gilles and Poirier are already four-time world medalists, having won silver in each of the past two seasons.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2133, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3670485216273487e-43, \"text\": \"Poirier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gilles\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"four-time world medalists\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"the past two seasons\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gilles and Poirier react after their free dance during the Milan Cortina Winter Olympics last month.Nathan Denette/The Canadian Press Both 34, the longtime partners are expected to retire from competition following Prague, though Gilles would not completely shut the door.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3670485216273487e-43, \"text\": \"Poirier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\"}, {\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"score\": 0.8153954872814404, \"rank\": 0.2263987421954181, \"text\": \"Milan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milan\"}, {\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4770570429352806e-15, \"text\": \"Cortina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}, {\"begin\": 2448, \"end\": 2454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"score\": 0.9981415865995672, \"rank\": 0.001861847371944663, \"text\": \"Prague\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prague\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gilles\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"their